* north mode : system to choose north direction
** 1st click : point 1
** 2nd click : point 2 : draw line & update north angle scroll
** use angle scroll to rotate line about its centre
** click either point to drag them around

* system to enter scale value, lock the scale values
* system to enter origin value, lock the origin values

* trees mode : output tree inputs as nice output file
* output file format update for sam as he needs
* keyboard shortcuts: zoom in/out, toggle tracking

